                     <join result="defendantPunishment" targOrder="Y" targets="t17940430-39-defend386 t17940430-39-punish204"></join>
               Imprisoned twelve months in the House of Correction
            </rs> and <rs id="t17940430-39-punish205" type="punishmentDescription">
